title: The Collected Battlefields (Dynamite|2008-13|Dgtl-TPB-HR|Empire)
description:
<a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Battlefields_%28comics%29" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Battlefields_%28comics%29</a>




Contains:

   The eight miniseries published to date, in Digital Hi-Res, compiled from the
   original omnibus edition and single-issue releases into homogeneous volumes,
   organized by narrative continuity, and each bookended with the trade edition
   cover in front and a cover gallery and/or bonus artwork in back.

   Plus separate author's notes
